    "4460429": {
      "title": "Membrane proteins bind lipids selectively to modulate their structure and function",
      "abstract": "A new mass-spectrometry method has been developed to obtain high-resolution spectra of folded proteins bound to lipids; using this technique as well as X-ray crystallography provides evidence for membrane protein conformational change as a result of lipid–protein interaction."
